argin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">联系人：刘永杰、胡荣艳</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">联系电话：0515-69057406、13626222271</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">日期：</span><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:\">日</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br /></p>','','','','','');
