fff; color:#000000; font-family:\">2.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院北区</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">（毓龙西路166号）</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">2.3招标内容：</span><span style=\"font-family:\">北区浮动盘管换热器更换换热管、1#立式半容积式热交换器更换换热管等维修项目，</span><span style=\"font-family:\">具体内容详见招标人要求和工程量清单</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">2.4发包方式：包工包料。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">3、投标人资格要求</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">3.1 投标</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">人</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">须是</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">具有建设行政主管部门核发的建筑机电安装工程专业承包三级及以上资质</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">的</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">独立法人</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">，</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">并具有</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">有效的安全生产许证</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">；</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"ba