color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">66696810</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:5pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:5pt; text-align:right; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:5pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:5pt; text-align:right; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">时间：</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">2020</span><span style=\"background-color:#f